An extension of PrintVisitor which will print the equations of a variable if required. The behavious of this class is determined by two modes PRINT_PARTIAL_EQNS and PRINT_VARIABLE_EQNS. When a variable or partial derivative is encountered then its equation may be printed. By default equations for PartialDerivatives are printed but equations for normal derivatives are not.
